channel.title: 🎧 The Way (Hum4n01d x T. C) Remix Competition!
channel.description:
Hello fellow Auxians! It’s been a little over a month since I released my newest track, a collaboration with @TC64, [The Way](http://soundcloud.com/hum4n01dmusic/the-way). We are now holding a competition to see who can come up with the best remix!
The winner of the competition will win: - A repost on both [Hum4n01d](https://soundcloud.com/hum4n01dmusic) and [T. C Music](https://soundcloud.com/toxiccaves64) to a total of 425 listeners - Access to project files for all songs by me and T. C - Eternal bragging rights :sunglasses:
If you’re in, let me know in this thread and I’ll DM you the full project :musical_note:
A demo of the song is available here: https://app.auxy.co/projects/hGle8WkUIPdwhri6AZS34g==
Can’t wait to hear what you guys come up with!
Deadline: March 31st, 2018
